# The live judge (/api/judge) runs a free, transparent heuristic by default —
# no API key required. Everything works out of the box.
#
# OPTIONAL: if you ever want the live tool to call a real frontier model instead
# of the built-in heuristic, set a provider key below and flip JUDGE_MODE=model.
# The key is read ONLY on the server (in app/api/judge/route.ts) and is never
# sent to the browser.
#
# JUDGE_MODE=heuristic        # "heuristic" (default, free) | "model"
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...       # only used when JUDGE_MODE=model
